有身為青梅的睦知道他的真實性格，但睦其實也不是會在意這個的人，他還會為祥子組樂團高興而開心。<br>全劇好似真的沒有人了解祥子的實際內心啊，初華肯定也不知道祥子憧憬他，甚至可能有點嫉妒羨慕著。<br>燈、祥子、立希三個人都自比蟲子，有著某種程度的自卑，仰望著陽光下的蝴蝶，只是外在表現方式不同。<br>燈用怪罪自己去封閉內心，立希用攻擊性去掩飾，祥子則是扮演心目中的陽角去假裝。渴望著蝴蝶，想成為蝴蝶，但仍然是個蟲子。", "ctime": "2023-08-16 21:32:21", "like": 192, "replies": [{"avatar": "/static/pic/i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/9d3a64598d5d43423642b01b5dd21d03dce5b760.jpg", "uname": "正义模仿者", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 0, "is_senior_member": 0, "message": "写得真好", "ctime": "2023-08-17 21:15:39", "like": 3}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/889257f57f267d192376bdfa3dfc819bfabdaf00.jpg", "uname": "朝倉理香子", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 1, "is_senior_member": 0, "message": "我是不是在贴吧看到你的评论了[doge]", "ctime": "2023-08-18 23:29:44", "like": 0}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i0.hdslb.com/bfs/face/member/noface.jpg", "uname": "tin0423", "current_level": 4, "vipStatus": 0, "is_senior_member": 0, "message": "回復 @朝倉理香子 :我也在貼吧回過別人類似的留言，但前面應該有加了點其他內容[吃瓜]", "ctime": "2023-08-18 23:40:41", "like": 0}], "sub_reply_entry_text": "共5条回复", "pictures": []}, {"avatar": "/static/pic/i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/e76a9420ff3f0053ede07d52cf87d69d17704d95.jpg", "pendant": "", "uname": "扭曲个体", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 1, "is_senior_member": 0, "user_sailing": {"id": 1689575325001, "name": "碧蓝航线礼服主题-评论背景", "image": "/static/pic/i0.hdslb.com/bfs/baselabs/op/dbeda59a57446b40ffb4df522796bdd3cf88a61ca3ea10dbbcc6f9f28d12ff24.png", "jump_url": "https://www.bilibili.com/h5/mall/equity-link/home?navhide=1&item_id=1689575325001&part=card_bg&f_source=garb&from=reply&vmid=19516837", "fan": {"is_fan": 1, "number": 1718, "color": "#A63B47", "name": "碧蓝航线礼服主题", "num_desc": "001718"}, "type": "suit"}, "message": "灯被立希抱着的时候还是想着去看祥子，跟立希相关的小细节还是那么难绷[笑哭]", "ctime": "2023-08-16 10:57:00", "like": 94, "replies": [{"avatar": "/static/pic/i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/dfe77fd9fb029011dbdde35e6960f652ead8ee84.jpg", "uname": "潜水修仙者", "current_level": 6, "vipStatus": 0, "is_senior_member": 0, "message": "c，又是一个没发现的细节……别迫害立希女士了呜呜呜[